hadiths[89]{hadithnumber,text}:
7048,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' (qiyamat ke din) mein hauze-kausar par hunga aur apne paas aaney walon ka intizar karta rahunga phir (hauze-kausar) par kuchh logon ko mujh tak pahunchne se pahley hi giraftaar kar liya jaeyga to main kahunga ke ye to meri ummat ke log hain. jawab milega ke aapko malum nahi ye log ultey paon phir gaey they. '' ibne-abi-Mulaika us hadis ko riwayat kartey waqt dua kartey ''aey Allah ! ham teri panah maangtey hain ke ham ultey paon phir jayen ya fitna mein pad jaaein.
7049,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''hauze-kausar par tum logon ka pesh khema hunga aur tum mein se kuchh log meri taraf aaeingey jab main unhein (hauz ka paanii) dene ke liye jhukoonga to unhein mere samney se kheench liya jaeyga mein kahunga aey mere rab! ye to meri ummat ke log hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga aapko malum nahi ke unhon-ne aap ke baad Deen mein kya kya nai baatein nikal li thiin.''
7050,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke main hauz kausar par tum se pahley rahunga jo wahan pahunchega to uska pani pieyga aur jo uska pani pi lega wo uske baad kabhi piyaasaa nahi hoga. mere paas aisey log bhi aaeingey jinhein main pehchanta hunga aur wo mujhey pehchantey hongey phir mere aur unke darmyan parda daal diya jaeyga abu-Hazim ne bayan kya ke Nauman bin abi Ayash ne bhi suna ke main unse ye hadis bayan kar raha hun to unhon-ne kaha ke kya tu ney Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah ye hadis suni thi? maine kaha ke haan. unhon-ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis isi tarah suni thi. abu-Saeed usmein itna badhaatey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye log mujh mein se hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us waqt kaha jaeyga ke aapko malum nahi ke aap ke baad unhon-ne kya tabdeeliyaan kar di thiin? mein kahunga ke doori ho doori ho unke liye jinhoney mere baad Deen mein tabdeeliyaan kar di thin. ''"
7051,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke main hauzey kausar par tum se pahley rahunga jo wahan pahunchega to uska pani pieye ga aur jo iska pani pi lega wo iske baad kabhi piyaasaa nahi hoga. mere paas aisey log bhi aaeingey jinhein main pehchanta hunga aur wo mujhey pehchantey hongey phir mere aur unke darmyan parda daal diya jaeyga abu-Hazim ne bayan kya ke Naumaan-bin-abii-ayaash ne bhi suna ke main unse ye hadis bayan kar raha hun to unhon-ne kaha ke kya tu ney Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah ye hadis suni thi? maine kaha ke haan. unhon-ne kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadis isi tarah suni thi. abu-Saeed usmein itna badhaatey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye log mujh mein se hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us waqt kaha jaeyga ke aapko malum nahi ke aap ke baad unhon-ne kya badlaaw (تبدیلیاں) kar diye they? main kahunga ke doori ho doori ho unke liye jinhoney mere baad Deen mein badlaaw (تبدیلیاں) kar diye they.''"
7052,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ''tum mere baad kuchh kaam aisey dekhogey jo tum ko burey lagein gey.'' sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap is silsiley mein kya hukm farmatey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''unhein unka haq ada karo aur apna haq Allah se maango.''
7053,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs apne ameer mein koi na-pasand baat dekhey to sabr karey (khaleefa ( ki itaat se agar koi baalisht bhar bhi bahar nikla to uski maut jahiliyat ki maut hogii.''
7054,"maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne apne ameer ki koi na-pasand cheez dekhi to usey chahey ke sabr karey isliye ke jisne jamat se aik baalisht bhar judai ikhtiyar ki aur usi haal mein maraa to wo jahiliyat ki si maut marey ga.''"
7055,ham Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein pahunchey wo mareez they aur ham ne arz kya : Allah Taala aapko sihat ata farmaaey. koi hadis bayan kijiye jiska nafa aapko Allah Taala pahunchaaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Lailatal-Aqbaa mein suna hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein bulaya aur ham ne aap se bait ki.
7056,"jin baton ka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se ahad liya tha unmein ye bhi tha ke khushi aur naa-gawaarii, tangi aur kushadgi aur apni haq talafi (تلفی) mein bhi itaat aur farmaanbardaarii karein aur ye bhi ke hukmaraanon ke sath hukumat ke barey mein us waqt tak jhagdaa na karein jab tak unko ea'laaniya kufr kartey na dekh lein. agar wo ea'laaniya kufr karein to tum ko Allah ke paas se daleel mil jaeygi."
7057,aik sahib (khud Usaid) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne falan Amr-bin-al-Aas ko Hakim bana diya aur mujhey nahi banaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log Ansari mere baad apni haq talafii (تلفی) dekhogey to qiyamat tak sabr karna yahan tak ke tum mujh se aa milo.
7058,main Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas Madina Munawra mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki masjid mein betha tha aur hamarey sath Marwan bhi tha. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine sabsey sachey insan se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ki tabahi Quraish ke chand ladkon ke hath se hogi. Marwan ne is par kaha un par Allah ki laanat ho. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar main unke khandan ke naam lekar batlaanaa chaahoon to batla sakta hun. phir jab bani Marwan Sham (Syria) ki hukumat par qaabiz ho gaey to main apne dada ke sath unki taraf jata tha. jab wahan unhon-ne naujawaan ladkon ko dekha to kaha ke shayad ye unhi mein se hun. ham ne kaha ke aapko zyada ilm hai.
7059,unhon-ne bayan kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) neend se bedaar huey to aap ka chehra surkh tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi. Arbon ki tabahi us balaa se hogi jo qareeb hi aa lagi hai. aaj yaajooj-maajooj ki diwar mein se itna suraakh ho gaya aur Sufiyan ne nawwey ya sou (100) ke adad ke liye ungli baandhii puchha gaya kya ham iske bawajud halaak ho jaeinge ke ham mein saaleheen bhi hongey? farmaya haan ! jab burai badh jaeygi (to aisa hi hoga).
7060,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke teelon mein se aik teeley par chadhey phir farmaya ke main jo kuchh dekhta hun tum bhi dekhtey ho? logon ne kaha ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main fitnon ko dekhta hun ke wo barish ke qatroo (قطروں) ki tarah tumharey gharon mein dakhil ho rahe hain.
7061,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''zamaana qareeb hota jaeyga aur amal kam hota jaeyga aur laalach dilon mein daal diya jaeyga aur fitney zahir honey lagein gey aur (هرج) ki kasarat ho jaeygi. ''logon ne sawal kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye (هرج) kya cheez hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qatl ! qatl ! aur Yunus aur Leis aur Zohri ke bhatijey ne bayan kya, unse Zohri ne, unse Humaid ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
7062,nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din se pahley aisey din hongey jin mein jahaalat utar padegii aur ilm utha liya jaeyga aur (هرج) badh jaeyga aur (هرج) qatl hai.''
7063,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din se pahley aisey din hongey jin mein jahaalat utar padegii aur ilm utha liya jaeyga aur (هرج) badh jaeyga aur (هرج) qatl hai.''
7064,Abdullah-bin-Masood aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) baithey aur guftgu kartey rahe phir abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat se pahley aisey din aaeingey jin mein ilm utha liya jaeyga aur jahaalat utar padegii aur (هرج) ki kasarat ho jaeygi aur (هرج) qatl hai.''
7065,main Abdullah-bin-Masood aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath betha hua tha to abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna usi tarah. (هرج) Habsha ki zaban mein qatl ko kehtey hain.
7066,"is hadis ko unhon-ne marfooan (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se siidhey taur per) bayan kya, kaha ke qiyamat se pahley (هرج) ke din hongey, unmein ilm khatm ho jaeyga aur jahaalat ghalib hogi. abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke habshi zaban main (هرج) ka maanaa qatl hai."
7067,aap wo hadis jantey hain jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (هرج) ke dinon wghaira ke mutaalliq bayan ki. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke wo bad-bakht tareen logon mein se hongey jinki zindagi mein qiyamat aaeygi.
7068,"ham Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur unse Hajjaj ke tarze amal ki shikayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke sabr karo kyonke tum par jo dour bhi aata hai to iske baad aaney wala dour is se bhi bura hoga yahan tak ke tum apne rab se ja milo. maine ye tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai."
7069,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke aik raat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghabraaey huey bedaar huey aur farmaya Allah ki zaat paak hai. Allah Taala ne kyaa-kyaa khazaaney nazil kiye hain aur kitney fitney utaarey hain un hujrey waaliyon ko koi bedaar kyon na karey aap ki murad paak beeviyon se thi taake ye Namaz padhein. bahut se duniya mein kapdey baareek pahn-ney waaliyaan aakhirat mein nangii hongii.
7070,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne ham musalmaanon par hathiyar uthaya wo ham se nahi hai.''
7071,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne ham musalmaanon par hathiyar uthaya wo ham se nahi hai.''
7072,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs apne kisi deeni bhai ki taraf hathiyar se ishara na karey kyonke wo nahi janta mumkin hai shaitan usey uske hath se chhudwaa de aur phir wo kisi musalman ko mar kar uski wjah se jahannam ke garhey mein gir padey.''
7073,maine Amr-bin-Dinar se kaha abu-Muhammad ! tum ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai ke unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik sahib teer lekar masjid mein se guzrey to unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teer ki nouk ka khayal rakho. Amr ne kaha ji haan maine suna hai.
7074,"aik sahib masjid mein teer lekar guzrey jinke phal bahar ko nikley huey they, to unhein hukm diya gaya ke unki nouk ka khayal rakhein ke wo kisi musalman ko zakhmi na kar dein."
7075,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tum mein se koi hamari masjid mein ya hamarey bazar mein guzrey aur uske paas teer hon to usey chahiye ke uski nouk ka khayal rakhey.'' ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne hath se unhein thaamey rahe. kahin kisi musalman ko us se koi takleef na pahunchey.
7076,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' musalman ko gali dena fisq (Allah ki naafarmaani) hai aur usko qatl karna kufr (Allah ka inkaar) hai.''
7077,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere baad kufr ki taraf na lot jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago."
7078,"aur aik doosrey shakhs (Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehmaan ( se bhi suna jo meri nazar mein Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-bakra se achchhey hain aur unse Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko qurbani ke din ko khutba diya aur farmaya ''tumhein malum hai ye kon sa din hai?'' logon ne kaha ke Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. bayan kya ke (iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khamoshi se) ham ye samjhey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska koi aur naam rakhengey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya ye qurbani ka din (yaum النحر) nahi hai?'' ham ne arz kya : kyon nahi, ya Rasulullah ! aap ne phir puchha ''ye kon sa Shahar hai? kya ye al-balda (Makka mukarrma) nahi hai?'' ham ne arz kya : kyon nahi, ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir tumhara khoon, tumharey maal, tumhari izzat aur tumhari khaal tum par isi tarah hurmat waley hain jis tarah is din ki hurmat is mahiney aur is Shahar mein hai. kya maine pahuncha diya ?'' ham ne kaha ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allah ! gawah rehna. isliye mera ye paigham maujood log ghair maujood logon ko pahuncha dein kyonke bahut se pahunchaney waley is paigham ko us tak pahunchaaein gey jo isko zyada mehfooz rakhney wala hoga.'' chunanche aisa hi hua aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere baad kaafir na ho jana ke kuchh, kuchh ki gardan maarney lago.'' phir jab wo din aaya jab Abdullah Amr-bin Hizrami ko jaariya-bin-qudaama ne aik makan mein gher kar jalaa diya to jaariya ne apne lashkar walon se kaha zara Abu-Bakra ko to jhaanko wo kis khayal mein hai. unhon-ne kaha ye Abu-Bakra maujood hain tum ko dekh rahe hain. Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-abii-bakra kehtey hain mujh se meri walida haala-binte-ghaleez ne kaha ke Abu-Bakra ne kaha agar ye log (jaariya ke lashkar waale) mere ghar mein bhi ghus aaein aur mujh ko maarney lagein to main un par aik baans ki chhadi bhi nahi chalaaunga."
7079,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere baad kaafir na ho jana ke tum mein kuchh, kuchh ki gardan maarney lagey.''"
7080,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par farmaya ke logon ko khamosh kar do. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere baad kaafir na ho jana ke tum aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lag jaao.''
7081,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''an-qareeb aisey fitney barpa hongey jin mein baithney wala khadey hone-waale se behtar hoga aur khada honey wala unmein chalney waley se behtar hoga aur chalney wala unmein daudney waley se behtar hoga, jo door se unki taraf jhank kar bhi dekhega to wo unko bhi samet lengey. us waqt jis kisi ko koi panah ki jagah mil jaey ya bachao ka maqam mil sakey wo usmein chala jaaey.''"
7082,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aisey fitney barpa hongey ke unmein baithney wala khadey hone-waale se behtar hoga aur khada honey wala chalney waley se behtar hoga aur chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga. agar koi unki taraf door se bhi jhank kar dekhega to wo usey bhi samet lengey aisey waqt jo koi us se koi panah ki jagah pa ley usey uski panah ley leni chaahiye.''
7083,"main aik martaba aapsii fasaadaat ke dinon mein main apne hathiyar laga kar nikla to Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se rastey mein mulaqat ho gaee. unhon-ne puchha kahan janey ka irada hai? maine kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha ke ladkey ki (jange-jamal aur siif'fiin mein) madad karni chahta hun, unhon-ne kaha lot jao. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke jab do musalman apni talwaaron ko lekar aamney samney muqaabla par aa jayen to donon dozakhi hain. puchha gaya ye to qaatil tha, maqtool ne kya, kiya (ke wo bhi jahannammii ho gayaa)? farmaya ke wo bhi apne muqabil ko qatl karne ka irada kiye huey tha. Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha ke phir maine ye hadis Ayub aur yoonus-bin-ubaid se zikr ki, mera maqsad tha ke ye donon bhi mujh se ye hadis bayan karein, un donon ne kaha ke is hadis ki riwayat Hasan Basri ne ahnaf-bin-Qais se aur unhon-ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se ki. ham se Sulaimaan-bin-Harb ne bayan kya kaha ham se Hammad-bin-Zaid ne yahi hadis bayan ki aur mua'mmal-bin-Hishaam ne kaha ke ham se Hammad-bin-Zaid ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ayyoob, Younus, Hisham aur muallaa-bin-Ziyaad ne imam Hasan Basri se bayan kya, unse ahnaf-bin-Qais aur unse Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur uski riwayat Mamar ne bhi Ayub se ki hai aur uski riwayat bakkaar-bin-abdul-Azeez ne apne bap se ki aur unse Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur ghander ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Mansoor ne, unse Rabai-bin-Hirash ne, unse Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. aur Sufiyan Sory ne bhi is hadis ko mansoor-bin-moa'tamir se riwayat kya, phir ye riwayat marfooaa nahi hai."
7084,"log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khair ke barey mein puchha kartey they lekin main shar ke barey mein poochhta tha. is khof se ke kahin meri zindagi mein hi shar na paida ho jaey. maine puchha : ya Rasulullah ! ham jahiliyat aur shar ke daur mein they phir Allah Taala ne hamein is khair se nawaza to kya is khair ke baad phir shar ka zamana hoga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. maine puchha : kya us shar ke baad phir khair ka zamana aayega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan lekin us khair mein kamzori hogi. maine puchha ke kamzori kya hogii? farmaya ke kuchh log hongey jo mere tareeqey ke khilaf chalein gey, unki kuchh baatein achi hongi lekin kuchh main tum burai dekhogey. maine puchha kya phir dourey khair ke baad dourey shar aayega? farmaya ke haan, jahannam ki taraf se bulaney waley dozakh ke darwazon par khadey hongey, jo unki baat maan lega wo usmein unhein jhatak dengey. maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! unki kuchh sifat bayan keejiye. farmaya ke wo hamarey hi jaisey hongey aur hamari hi zaban (arabii) boleyn gey . maine puchha : phir agar maine wo zamana paya to aap mujhey unke barey mein kya hukm detey hain? farmaya ke musalmaanon ki jamat aur unke imam ke sath rehna. maine kaha ke agar muslamaanon ki jamat na ho aur na unka koi imam ho? farmaya ke phir un tamam logon se alag ho kar chahe tumhen jangal mein ja kar darakhton ki jadein chabaani (چبانی) parrey yahan tak ke usi haalat mein tumhari maut aa jaey."
7085,"ahale-Madeena ka aik lashkar taiyaar kya gaya (yani Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein Sham (Syria) walon se muqaabla karne ke liye) aur mera naam usmein likh diya gaya. phir main Ikrima se mila aur maine unhein khabar di to unhon-ne mujhey shirkat se sakhti ke sath mana kya. phir kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di hai ke kuchh musalman jo mushrekeen ke sath rahtey they wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khilaf (jangoon) mein mushrekeen ki jamat ki zyadti ka baais bantey . phir koi teer aata aur unmein se kisi ko lag jata aur qatl kar deta ya unhein koi talwaar se qatl kar detaa, phir Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (إن الذين توفاهم الملائكة ظالمي أنفسهم‏) '' bila shak wo log jinko Farishtey faut kartey hain us haal mein ke wo apni jaanon par zulm karne waley hotey hain.''"
7086,"ham se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 hadison farmai thin jin mein se aik to maine dekh li dusri ka intizar hai. ham se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke amanat logon ke dilon ki jadoon mein nazil hui thi phir logon ne usey Quran se seekhaa, phir sunnat se seekha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se amanat ke uth janey ke mutaalliq farmaya tha ke aik shakhs aik neend soeyga aur amanat uske dil se nikal di jaeygi aur iska nishan aik dhabbey jitna baqi reh jaeyga phir wo aik neend soeyga aur phir amanat nikaalii jaeygi to iske dil mein aabley ki tarah iska nishan baqi reh jaeyga, jaisey tum ne koi chingaarii apne paon par gira li ho aur uski wjah se aabla pad jaey, tum usmein soojan dekhogey lekin andar kuchh nahi hoga aur log khareed w farokht karengey lekin koi amanat ada karne wala nahi hoga. phir kaha jaeyga ke falan qabeeley mein aik amanat daar aadmi hai aur kisi ke mutaalliq kaha jaeyga ke wo kis qadr aqlmand, kitna khush tabiat ka, kitna dilaawar aadmi hai halanke uske dil mein raai ke daney ke barabar bhi eman na hoga aur mujh par aik zamana guzar gaya aur main uski parwaa nahi karta tha ke tum mein se kis ke sath mein lein-dein karta hun agar wo musalman hota to uska Islam usey mere haq ke ada karne par majbur karta aur agar wo nasrani hota to iske Hakim log usko dabaatey emaandari par majbur kartey. lekin aaj kal to main sirf falan-falan logon se hi lein-dein karta hun."
7087,"wo Hajjaj ke yahan gaey to usne kaha ke aey ibne- Akwa' ! tum gaaun mein rehney lagey ho kya ultey paon phir gaey? kaha ke nahi balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey jangal mein rehney ki ijazat di thi aur Yazeed bin abi Ubaid se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke jab Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) Shahid kiye gaey to Salma bin Akwa' (Raziallahu anhu) Rabza chaley gaey aur wahan aik aurat se shadi kar li aur wahan unke bachchey bhi paida huey. wo barabar wahin par rahe, yahan tak ke wafat se chand din pahley Madina aagey they."
7088,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''wo waqt qareeb hai ke musalman ka behtreen maal wo bakriyan hongi jinhein wo lekar pahaadii ki chotiyon aur barish barasney ki jaghon par chala jaeyga wo fitnon se apne Deen ki hifazat ke liye wahan bhag kar aa jaaeyga.''
7089,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon se sawalat kiye. aakhir jab log baar-baar sawal karne lagey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par aik din chadhey aur farmaya ke aaj tum mujh se jo sawal bhi karogey main tumhen iska jawab doonga . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main daaein-baaein dekhney laga to har shakhs ka sar uske kapdey mein chipa hua tha aur wo ro raha tha. aakhir aik shakhs ne khamoshi todii. uska jab kisi se jhagdaa hota to unhein unke bap ke siwa doosrey bap ki taraf pukara jata. unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! mere walid kon hain? farmaya tumharey walid Huzafa hain. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) samney aaey aur arz kya ham Allah se ke wo rab hai, Islam se ke wo Deen hai, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke wo rasool hain razi hain aur aazmaish ki burai se ham Allah ki panah maangtey hain. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine khair w shar aaj jaisa dekha, kabhi nahi dekha tha. mere samney jannat w dozakh ki sura pesh ki gaee aur maine unhein diwar ke qareeb dekha. Qatada ne bayan kya ke ye baat is aayat ke sath zikr ki jati hai يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تسألوا an (an) أشياء إن تبد لكم تسؤكم‏ ke ''aey logo ! jo eman laey ho aisi chizon ke barey mein sawal na karo agar wo zahir kar di jayen to tumhen buri malum hoon.''"
7090,aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha har shakhs kapdey mein apna sar lapetey huey ro raha tha aur fitney se Allah ki panah maang raha tha ya yun keh raha tha ke main Allah se fitne ki burai se panah mangta hun.
7091,"phir yahi hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql ki, usmein bajaey (soo) ke (shar) ka lafz hai."
7092,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member ke aik taraf khadey huey aur farmaya ''fitna idhar hai, fitna idhar hai jidhar se shaitan ka seeng tuloo hota hai ya suraj ka seeng farmaya''"
7093,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mashriq ki taraf rukh kiye huey they aur farma rahe they '' aagah ho jao, fitna us taraf hai jidhar se shaitan ka seeng tuloo hota hai.''"
7094,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Allaah! hamarey mulk Sham (Syria) mein hamein barkat de, hamarey Yaman mein hamein barkat de.'' sahaba ne arz kya aur hamarey Najad mein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ''aey Allah hamarey Sham (Syria) mein barkat de, hamein hamarey Yaman mein barkat de.'' sahaba ne kaha aur hamarey Najad mein? mera guman hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri martaba farmaya '' wahan zalzaley aur fitney hain aur wahan shaitan ka seeng tuloo hoga.''"
7095,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas aaey to ham ne ummeed ki ke wo ham se koi achi baat karengey. itney mein aik sahib hakeem naam ke ham se pahley unke paas pahunch gaey aur puchha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! ham se zamana fitne mein qitaal ke mutaalliq hadis bayan keejiye. Allah Taala farmata hai tum unse jang karo yahan tak ke fitna baqi na rahe. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tumhen malum bhi hai ke fitna kya hai? tumhari maan tumhen roey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fitna rafa' karne ke liye mushrekeen se jang kartey they, shirk mein padnaa ye fitna hai. kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ladai tum logon ki tarah badhshahat hasil karne ke liye hoti thi?"
7096,"ham umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke unhon-ne puchha : tum mein se kisey fitne ke barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman yad hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke insan ka fitna (aazmaaish) uski beewii, uske maal, uske bachchey aur padosi ke maamlaat mein hota hai jiska kaffara namaaz, sadqa, bhalai ka hukm aur burai se rokna kar deta hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main iske mutaalliq nahi poochhta balke us fitne ke barey mein poochhta hun jo dariya ki tarah thaathein maarega. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ameerul-momineen aap par iska koi khatrah nahi iske aur aap ke darmyan aik band darwaza rukawat hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha kya wo darwaza tod diya jaeyga ya khola jaaeyga? bayan kya tod diya jaeyga umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke phir to wo kabhi band na ho sakega. maine kaha ji haan. ham ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) us darwaze ke mutaalliq jantey they? farmaya ke haan, jis tarah main janta hun ke kal se pahley raat aaeygii kyonke maine aisi baat bayan ki thi jo be-buniyaad nahi thi. hamein unse ye poochhtey huey dar laga ke wo darwaza kon they. chunanche ham ne Masruq se kaha (ke wo poochhein) jab unhon-ne puchha ke wo darwaza kon they? to unhon-ne kaha ke wo darwaza umr (Raziallahu anhu) they."
7097,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina ke baghaat mein kisi baagh ki taraf apni kisi zarurat ke liye gaey, main bhi aap ke peechhey-peechhey gaya. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein dakhil huey to main iske darwazey par baith gaya aur apne dil mein kaha ke aaj main aap ka darbaan banoonga halanke aap ne mujhey iska hukm nahi diya tha. aap andar chaley gaey aur apni haajat poori ki. phir aap kunwein ki munder par baith gaey aur apni donon pindliyon ko khol kar unhein kunwein mein latkaa liya. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur andar janey ki ijazat chahi . maine unse kaha ke aap yahin rahein, main aap ke liye ijazat lekar aata hun. chunanche wo khadey rahe aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar arz kya : ya Nabi Allaah! Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke paas aaney ki ijazat chahtey hain. farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat suna do. chunanche wo andar aagey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki daain taraf aa kar unhon-ne bhi apni pindliyon ko khol kar kunein mein latkaa liya. itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaey. maine kaha thehro main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat ley loon (aur maine andar ja kar aap se arz kya) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unko bhi ijazat de aur jannat ki khushkhabri bhii. khair wo bhi aaey aur usi kunwein ki mundeer par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baain taraf baithey aur apni pindliyaan khol kar kunein mein latkaa din. aur kunwein ki mundeer bhar gaee aur wahan jagah na rahi. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur maine unse bhi kaha ke yahin rahiye yahan tak ke aap ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat maang loon. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat do aur jannat ki bashaarat de do aur uske sath aik aazmaish hai jo unhein pahunchegii. phir wo bhi dakhil huey, unke sath baithney ke liye koi jagah na thi. chunanche wo ghoom kar unke samney kunein ke kinarey par aagey phir unhon-ne apni pindliyaan khol kar kunwein mein paon latkaa liye, phir mere dil mein bhai (ghaaliban abu-Barda ya abu-Raham) ki tamanna paida hui aur main dua karne laga ke wo bhi aa jatey, ibne-Musaiyab ne bayan kya ke maine us se unki qabron ki tabeer li ke sab ki qabrein aik jagah hongi lekin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki alag Baqee gharqad mein hai."
7098,"Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke aap (Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu)) se guftgu kyon nahi kartey (ke aam musalmanon ki shikaayaton ka khayal rakhein ( unhon-ne kaha ke maine (khilwat mein) unse guftgu ki hai lekin (fitne ke) darwaze ko kholey baghair ke is tarah main sabse pahley us darwaza ko kholney wala hunga main aisa aadmi nahi hun ke kisi shakhs se jab wo 2 aadmiyon par ameer bana diya jaey ye kahun ke to sabse behtar hai. jabke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sun chuka hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ko (qiyamat ke din) laya jaeyga aur usey aag mein daal diya jaeyga phir wo usmein is tarah chakkii peesega jaisey gadhaa peestaa hai. phir dozakh ke log iske charon taraf jama ho jaeinge aur kahengey, aey fulaan! kya tum nekiyon ka hukm kartey aur buraaiyon se rokaa nahi kartey they? wo shakhs kahega ke main achi baat ke liye kehta to zaroor tha lekin khud nahi karta tha aur buri baat se roktaa bhi tha lekin khud karta tha."
7099,jange-jamal ke zamane mein mujhey aik kalime ne fayda pahunchaya jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke Faaris ki saltanat walon ne boraan naam ke Kisraa ki beti ko badshah bana liya hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo qaum kabhi falaah nahi paaeygii jiski hukumat aik aurat ke hath mein ho.
7100,"ham se Abdullah-bin Muhammad ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se Yahyaa-bin-Aadam ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se abu-Bakar-bin-Ayaash ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se abu-Haseen ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se abu-Maryam Abdullah-bin Ziyad al-Asadii ne bayan kya ke jab Tal'ha, Zuber aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Basra ki taraf rawaana huey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammaar-bin-Yaasir aur Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhejaa. ye donon buzurg hamarey paas Kufa aaey aur member par chadhey. Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) member ke uper sabse unchi jagah they aur Ammaar-bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) unse nichey they. phir ham unke paas jama ho gaey aur maine Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey suna ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Basra gaee hain aur Allah ki qism wo duniya aur aakhirat main tumharey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak biwi hain lekin Allah tabarak w taala ne tumhen aazmaya hai taake jaan ley ke tum us Allah ki itaat kartey ho ya Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki."
7101,Kufa mein Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) member par khadey huey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur unki rawaangii ka zikr kya aur kaha ke bila shubah wo duniya aur aakhirat main tumharey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi hain lekin tum unke barey mein aazmaey gaey ho.
7102,abu-Musa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey jab unhein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ahale-koofa ke paas isliye bheja tha ke logon ko ladney ke liye taiyaar karein. abu-Musa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey jab se tum muslmaan huey ho ham ne koi baat us se zyada buri nahi dekhi jo tum is kaam mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya maine bhi jab se tum donon musalman huey ho tumhari koi baat is se buri nahi dekhi jo tum us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) donon ko eik-eik kapdey ka nayaa joda pahnaayaa phir teenon mil kar masjid mein tashrif ley gaey.
7103,abu-Moosa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey jab unhein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ahale-koofa ke paas isliye bheja tha ke logon ko ladney ke liye taiyaar karein. abu-Musa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey jab se tum muslmaan huey ho ham ne koi baat us se zyada buri nahi dekhi jo tum is kaam mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya maine bhi jab se tum donon musalman huey ho tumhari koi baat is se buri nahi dekhi jo tum us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) donon ko eik-eik kapdey ka nayaa joda pahnaayaa phir teenon mil kar masjid mein tashrif ley gaey.
7104,abu-Moosa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar bin-Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey jab unhein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ahale-koofa ke paas isliye bheja tha ke logon ko ladney ke liye taiyaar karein. abu-Musa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) donon Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey jab se tum muslmaan huey ho ham ne koi baat us se zyada buri nahi dekhi jo tum is kaam mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya maine bhi jab se tum donon musalman huey ho tumhari koi baat is se buri nahi dekhi jo tum us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) donon ko eik-eik kapdey ka nayaa joda pahnaayaa phir teenon mil kar masjid mein tashrif ley gaey.
7105,"main abu-Masood, abu-Musa aur Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath betha hua tha. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha hamarey sath waley jitney log hain main agar chaahoon to tumharey siwa unmein se har aik ka kuchh na kuchh aib bayan kar sakta hun. (lekin tum aik be-aeib ho) aur jab se tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki, maine koi aib ka kaam tumhara nahi dekha. aik yahi aib ka kaam dekhta hun, tum us daur mein yani logon ko jang ke liye uthaney mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) tum se aur tumharey sathi abu-Musa Ash-ari se jab se tum donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki hai maine koi aib ka kaam us se zyada nahi dekha jo tum donon us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. is par Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur wo maaldaar aadmi they ke ghulam ! 2 hulley laao. chunanche unhon-ne aik hulla abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya aur doosra Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur kaha ke aap donon bhai kapdey pahan kar Juma padhney chalein ."
7106,"main abu-Masood, abu-Musa aur Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath betha hua tha. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha hamarey sath waley jitney log hain main agar chaahoon to tumharey siwa unmein se har aik ka kuchh na kuchh aib bayan kar sakta hun. (lekin tum aik be-aeib ho) aur jab se tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki, maine koi aib ka kaam tumhara nahi dekha. aik yahi aib ka kaam dekhta hun, tum us daur mein yani logon ko jang ke liye uthaney mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) tum se aur tumharey sathi abu-Musa Ash-ari se jab se tum donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki hai maine koi aib ka kaam us se zyada nahi dekha jo tum donon us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. is par Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur wo maaldaar aadmi they ke ghulam ! 2 hulley laao. chunanche unhon-ne aik hulla abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya aur doosra Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur kaha ke aap donon bhai kapdey pahan kar Juma padhney chalein ."
7107,"main abu-Masood, abu-Musa aur Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath betha hua tha. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha hamarey sath waley jitney log hain main agar chaahoon to tumharey siwa unmein se har aik ka kuchh na kuchh aib bayan kar sakta hun. (lekin tum aik be-aeib ho) aur jab se tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki, maine koi aib ka kaam tumhara nahi dekha. aik yahi aib ka kaam dekhta hun, tum us daur mein yani logon ko jang ke liye uthaney mein jaldi kar rahe ho. Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) tum se aur tumharey sathi abu-Musa Ash-ari se jab se tum donon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ikhtiyar ki hai maine koi aib ka kaam us se zyada nahi dekha jo tum donon us kaam mein der kar rahe ho. is par Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur wo maaldaar aadmi they ke ghulam ! 2 hulley laao. chunanche unhon-ne aik hulla abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ko diya aur doosra Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ko aur kaha ke aap donon bhai kapdey pahan kar Juma padhney chalein ."
7108,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab Allah kisi qaum par azab nazil karta hai to azab un sab logon par aata hai jo us qaum mein hotey hain phir unhein unke aamaal ke mutabiq uthaya jaaeyga.''
7109,"aur meri unse mulaqat Kufa mein hui thi. wo ibne-shabarma ke paas aaey aur kaha ke mujhey Esa (Mansoor ke bhai aur Kufa ke waali) ke paas ley chalo taake main usey nasihat karun. ghaaliban ibne- shabarma ne khof mehsus kya aur nahi ley gaey. unhon-ne is par bayan kya ke ham se Hasan Basri ne bayan kya ke jab Hasan-bin-Ali ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaf lashkar lekar nikley to Amr-bin-al-Aas ne ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke main aisa lashkar dekhta hun jo us waqt tak wapas nahi ja sakta jab tak apne muqabil ko bhagaa na ley. phir ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke musalmanon ke ahal w ayaal ka kon kafeel hoga? jawab diya ke main, phir Abdullah-bin Aamir aur Abdur-Rehman bin Samra ne kaha ke ham Ameer-Muaawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se miltey hain (aur unse suleh ke liye kehtey hain) Hasan Basri ne kaha ke maine Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they ke Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mera ye betaa saiyed hai aur ummeed hai ke iske zariey Allah musalmanon ki 2 jamaton mein suleh kara dega."
7110,"maine Hurmala ko dekha tha Hurmala ne bayan kya ke mujhey Usama ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bheja aur mujh se kaha, us waqt tum se Ali (Raziallahu anhu) poochhengey ke tumharey sathi (Usaama (Raziallahu anhu)) jange-jamal w safein se kyon peechhey reh gaey they, to unse kehna ke unhon-ne aap se kaha hai ke agar aap sher ke munh mein hon tab bhi mein usmein bhi aap ke sath rahoon lekin ye mamla hi aisa hai yani musalmanon ki aapas ki jang to (is mein shirkat saheeh) nahi malum hui (hurmala kehtey hain ke) chunanche unhon-ne koi cheez nahi di. phir main Hasan, Husain aur Abdullah-bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unhon-ne meri sawari par itna maal ladwaa diya jitna ke oont utha na sakta tha."
7111,"jab ahale-Madeena ne Yazeed bin Muawiya ki bait se inkar kya to Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne khaadimon aur ladkon ko jama kya aur kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har ghadr karne waley ke liye qiyamat ke din aik jhanda khada kya jaeyga aur ham ne us shakhs ( Yazeed ( ki bait , Allah aur uske rasool ke naam par ki hai aur mere ilm mein koi ghadr us se badh kar nahi hai ke kisi shakhs se Allah aur uske rasool ke naam par bait ki jaey aur phir us se jang ki jaey aur dekho Madina waalo! tum mein se jo koi Yazeed ki bait ko todey aur doosrey kisi se bait karey to mujh main aur is mein koi talluq nahi raha, mein us se alag hun."
7112,"jab Abdullah-bin Ziyad aur Marwan Sham (Syria) mein they aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne Makka mein aur khawaarij ne Basra mein qabza kar liya tha to main apne walid ke sath abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya. jab ham unke ghar mein aik kamre ke saaye mein baithey huey they jo baans ka bana hua tha, ham unke paas baith gaey aur mere walid unse baat karne lagey aur kaha : aey abu-Barza! aap nahi dekhtey log kin baton mein aafat aur ikhtilaf mein ulajh gaey hain. maine unki zaban se sabse pehli baat ye suni ke main jo in Quraish ke logon se naraz hun to mahz Allah ki raza mandi ke liye, Allah mera ajr dene wala hai. Arab ke logo! tum jantey ho pahley tumhara kya haal tha tum gumrahi mein giraftaar they, Allah ne Islam ke zariey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zariey tum ko is buri haalat se nijat di. yahan tak ke tum is rutbe ko pahunchey. (duniyaa ke Hakim aur sardaar bin gaey) phir usi duniya ne tum ko kharaab kar diya. dekho! ye shakhs jo Sham (Syria) mein Hakim bin betha hai yani Marwan duniya ke liye lad raha hai. ye log jo tumharey samney hain. ( khawaarij ( Allah ki qism ! ye log sirf duniya ke liye lad rahe hain aur wo jo Makka mein hai Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) , Allah ki qism ! wo bhi sirf duniya ke liye lad raha hai."
7113,aaj kal ke munafiq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney ke munaafeqeen se badtar hain. us waqt chhipaatey they aur aaj iska khullam khullaa izhar kar rahe hain.
7114,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein nifaq tha aaj to eman ke baad kufr ikhtiyar karna hai.
7115,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat qaaim na hogi yahan tak ke aik shakhs doosrey ki qabr ke paas se guzrega aur kahega, kash! main usi ki jagah hota. ''"
7116,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke qabila dos ki aurton ka zul-khalasa ka ( tawaaf kartey huey) koolhey se koolhey chhilley aur zul-khalasa qabila dos ka but tha jis ko wo zamana jahiliyat mein puja kartey they.
7117,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi yahan tak ke qahtaan ka aik shakhs ( badshah bin kar) niklega aur logon ko apne dandey se haankega.''
7118,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat qaaim na hogi yahan tak ke sar zameene-hijaaz se aik aag niklegii aur Basra mein oonton ki gardanon ko roshan kar degi. ''
7119,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''an-qareeb dariyaaey Furaat se soney ka aik khazaana niklega to jo koi wahan maujood ho wo usmein se kuchh na ley.''
7120,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' sadqa karo kyonke an-qareeb logon par aik aisa zamana aayega jab aik shakhs apna sadqa lekar phirega aur koi usey leney wala nahi milega.'' Musaddad ne bayan kya ke Harisa Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ke maan-shareek bhai they."
7121,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak 2 azeem jamatein jang na karengii. un donon jamaton ke darmyan badi khoonrezii hogi. halanke donon ka dawa aik hi hoga aur yahan tak ke bahut se jhootey dajjal bhejey jaengey. taqriban tees dajjaal. unmein se har aik dawa karega ke wo Allah ka rasool hai aur yahan tak ke ilm utha liya jaeyga aur zalzalon ki kasarat hogi aur zamana qareeb ho jaeyga aur fitney zahir ho jaeinge aur haraj badh jaeyga aur haraj se murad qatl hai aur yahan tak ke tumharey paas maal ki kasarat ho jaeygi balke bah padega aur yahan tak ke saahibe-maal ko uska fikr daamangeer hoga ke iska sadqa qabool kon karey aur yahan tak ke wo pesh karega lekin jiske samney pesh karega wo kahega ke mujhey uski zarurat nahi hai aur yahan tak ke log badi badii imaaraton par aapas mein fakhr karengey. aik se aik badh chadh kar Imaarat banaaeingey aur yahan tak ke aik shakhs doosrey ki qabr se guzrega aur kahega ke kash! main bhi usi jagah hota aur yahan tak ke suraj maghrib se niklega. to jab wo is tarah tuloo hoga aur log dekh lengey to sab eman ley aaeingey lekin ye wo waqt hoga jab kisi aisey shakhs ko uska eman lana fayda na pahunchaaeyga jo pahley se eman na laya ho ya us ne apne eman ke sath achchhey kaam na kiye hun aur qiyamat achcha is tarah qaaim ho jaeygi ke 2 aadmiyon ne apne darmyan kapda phaila rakha hoga aur usey abhi bech na paaey hongey na lapet paaey hongey aur qiyamat is tarah barpa ho jaeygi ke aik shakhs apni ontni ka doodh nikal kar wapas hua hoga ke usey kha bhi na paya hoga aur qiyamat is tarah qaaim ho jaeygi ke wo apne hauz ko durust kar raha hoga aur is mein se pani bhi na piyaa hoga aur qiyamat is tarah qaaim ho jaeygi ke usne apna luqma munh ki taraf uthaya hoga aur abhi usey khaya bhi na hoga.
7122,"dajjal ke barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jitna maine puchha utnaa kisi ne nahi puchha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya tha ke us se tumhen kya nuqsan pahunchega. maine arz kya ke log kehtey hain ke iske sath roti ka pahaad aur pani ki nehar hogi, farmaya ke wo Allah par us se bhi zyada aasan hai."
7123,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''dajjaal dahini aankh se kaana hoga uski aankh kya hai maano phoolaa hua angoor.''
7124,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''dajjaal aayega aur Madina ke aik kinarey qiyam karega, phir Madina teen martaba kaanpega aur uske nateejey mein har kaafir aur munafiq nikal kar uski taraf chala jaaeyga.''"
7125,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Madeena walon par dajjal ka raub nahi padega us din Madina ke saat (7) darwazey hongey har darwazey par 2 Farishtey ( pahra detey ( hongey. ''
7126,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Madina par Masih dajjal ka raub nahi padega . us waqt uske saat (7) darwazey hongey aur har darwazey par pahredaar 2 Farishtey hongey. '' Ali-bin-Abdullaah ne kaha ke Muhammad-bin Ishaq ne Saleh bin Ibrahim se riwayat kya, unse unke walid Ibrahim bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne bayan kya ke main Basra gaya to mujh se Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahi hadis bayan ki."
7127,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein khadey huey aur Allah ki tareef uski shaan ke mutabiq bayan ki. phir dajjal ka zikr farmaya ke main tumhen us se daraataa hun aur koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne apni qaum ko us se na daraayaa ho, albatta main tumhen iske barey mein aik baat bataataa hun jo kisi Nabi ne apni qaum ko nahi batai thi aur wo ye ke wo kaana hoga aur Allah Taala kaana nahi hai."
7128,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main soyaa hua ( khuwab mein) Kaba ka tawaaf kar raha tha ke aik sahib jo gehunwey rang ke they aur unke sar ke baal seedhey they aur sar se pani tapak raha tha (un par meri nazar padi ( maine puchha ye kon hain? mere sath ke logon ne bataya ke ye Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) hain phir maine mud kar dekha to motey shakhs par nazar padi jo surkh tha uske baal ghunghraaley they, aik aankh ka kaana tha, uski aik aankh angoor ki tarah uthi hui thi. logon ne bataya ke ye dajjal hai. uski sura abdul-Uzzaa bin qatan se bahut miltii thi."
7129,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap apni Namaz mein dajjal ke fitney se panah maangtey they."
7130,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dajjal ke barey mein farmaya ke iske sath pani aur aag hogi aur uski aag thanda pani hogi aur pani aag hoga. Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine bhi ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai.
7131,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo Nabi bhi maboos kya gaya to unhon-ne apni qaum ko kaaney jhootey se daraayaa , aagah raho ke wo kaana hai aur tumhara rab kaana nahi hai. aur uski donon aankhon ke darmyan '' kaafir '' likha hua hai.'' is baab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis riwayat ki hai."
7132,"aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se dajjal ke mutaalliq aik lambi hadis bayan ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshadat mein ye bhi tha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dajjal aayega aur uske liye naa-mumkin hoga ke Madina ki ghatiyon mein dakhil ho. chunanche wo Madina Munawra ke qareeb kisi shor wali zameen par qiyam karega. phir us din uske paas aik mard momin jaeyga aur wo afzal tareen logon mein se hoga aur us se kahega ke main gawahi deta hun is baat ki jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se bayan farmaya tha. is par dajjal kahega kya tum dekhtey ho agar main usey qatl kar dun aur phir zinda karun to kya tumhen mere maamle mein shak w shuba baqi rahega? uske paas waley log kahengey ke nahi, chunanche wo us sahib ko qatl kar dega aur phir usey zinda kar dega. ab wo sahib kahengey ke Allah ki qasam! aaj se zyada mujhey terey mamley mein pahley itni baseerat hasil na thi. is par dajjal phir unhein qatl karna chaahega lekin is martaba usey mar na sakega.''"
7133,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Madina Munawra ke raston par Farishtey pahra detey hain na yahan taaoon aa sakti hai aur na dajjal aa sakta hai.''
7134,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''dajjaal Madina tak aayega to yahan farishton ko uski hifazat kartey huey paaeyga chunanche na dajjal uske qareeb aa sakta hai aur na taaoon, inshaAllah .''"
7135,"aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas ghabraaey huey dakhil huey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke tabahi hai Arbon ke liye us burai se jo qareeb aa chuki hai. aaj yaajooj maajooj ki diwar se itna khul gaya hai aur aap ne apne angoothey aur uski qareeb wali ungli ko mila kar aik halqa banaya. itna sun kar Zenab bin Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! to kya ham iske bawajud halaak ho jaeinge ke ham mein nek Saleh log bhi zinda hongey ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jab burai bahut badh jaeygi."
7136,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ( سد ( yani yaajooj maajooj ki diwar itni khul gaee hai.'' Wuhaib ne nawwey ka ishara karke batlaya .
